OL,3,C'Enough is enough': Farmers hit out at
OL,4,Cextra red tape post-Brexit
OL,6,FChannel Islands' farmers say they are
OL,7,Ffrustrated that "layers of
OL,8,Fbureaucracy" and red tape post-Brexit
OL,9,Fare causing major challenges across
OL,10,Fthe industry.
OL,12,FThey add policies created after
OL,13,FBritain left the European Union have
OL,14,Fcaused delays in shipping essential
OL,15,Fitems such as seeds and machinery,
OL,16,Fwith imports from Europe that used to
OL,17,Ftake two to three weeks now taking up
OL,18,Fto eight.
