OL,3,C'Enough is enough': Farmers hit out at
OL,4,Cextra red tape post-Brexit
OL,6,FGuernsey Dairy's Julian Ogier said:
OL,7,F"When we're buying directly from the
OL,8,FEU, you may be told it's been
OL,9,Fdispatched but then a few days later
OL,10,Ftold it's been returned to the
OL,11,Fsupplier because the paperwork wasn't
OL,12,Fcorrect".
OL,14,FJersey Dairy has taken the step to
OL,15,Ffocus its trade on the UK and Asian
OL,16,Fmarkets to "minimise the impact of
OL,17,FBrexit".
OL,19,FManaging Director Eamon Fenlon added:
OL,20,F"There's so many different negative
OL,21,Faspects to Brexit that add cost".
