OL,3,C'Enough is enough': Farmers hit out at
OL,4,Cextra red tape post-Brexit
OL,6,FOther businesses, such as Jersey's
OL,7,FMaster Farms, have also said Brexit
OL,8,Fcan drive running costs up by over 5%.
OL,10,FHead of Jersey's Farming Association
OL,11,FDoug Richardson said: "Layers of
OL,12,Fbureaucracy seem to be added all the
OL,13,Ftime.
OL,15,F"We are at a point now where it's
OL,16,Fprobably fair to say enough is enough."
