OL,3,C'Enough is enough': Farmers hit out at
OL,4,Cextra red tape post-Brexit
OL,6,FJersey's Environment Minister, Deputy
OL,7,FSteve Luce, said the Channel Islands
OL,8,Fabide by similar rules to the UK post-
OL,9,FBrexit which has brought some extra
OL,10,Fchecks.
OL,12,FHe added: "Our aim is to achieve the
OL,13,Fright levels of protection for animal,
OL,14,Fplant and human health, but to balance
OL,15,Fthat with minimising restrictions on
OL,16,Ftrade and avoiding over-cumbersome red
OL,17,Ftape.
