OL,3,C'Enough is enough': Farmers hit out at
OL,4,Cextra red tape post-Brexit
OL,6,F"We're working closely with DEFRA to
OL,7,Fensure we're consistent on what are
OL,8,Fdeemed to be potentially risky
OL,9,Fimports, and will adopt similar checks
OL,10,Fon produce and documentation."
OL,12,FThe Minister explained that officials
OL,13,Fare working on a 'trusted trader'
OL,14,Fscheme that would allow some
OL,15,Fbusinesses to streamline paperwork on
OL,16,Fregular imports.
OL,18,FITV News has contacted Guernsey's
OL,19,Fgovernment for comment.
